      <title>中国，日本，韩国更新自由贸易电话，誓言建立联系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/china-japan-s-korea-renew-free-trade-call-vow-to-build-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[来自中国，日本和韩国的贸易负责人更新了呼吁开放，公平的商品流，并承诺加深经济联系，前几天，特朗普政府将释放全球各国的新鲜关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/china-japan-s-korea-renew-free-trade-call-vow-to-build-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 03:46:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
